content.rendered:
The French Bistro Dining Table is a table made with mild steel legs and a textured walnut wooden top, some parts show evidence of the welding process; This enhances the attraction of the table legs, making it a unique feature. 

The French Bistro Dining Table and its related items are very popular with cafe’s, bars, restaurants and many other venues. 

The French Bistro table legs can come in any colour – POA

Suitable for indoor use. Held in stock for delivery in 3-4 days. 1 Year structural guarantee on the French Bistro Items & a 1 year guarantee on the finish/lacquer.
